1.70 2016-05-03T23:23:27+02:00 (83cb6b1 => abeltje)
 - (abeltje) Resolve a backward incompatibilty
 -     In pre 1.70 Test::Smoke 'sync_type' was the way to specify what sync
 -     method to use. In 1.70 this became 'syncer', now switched back to
 -     'sync_type'.

 - (H.Merijn Brand - Tux) Spelling error

 - (abeltje) Add versions to all the new modules

